    <note>Shen(2) Zhou [7323] His ancestors were a Wuxing jun, Wukang xian Shen(2) lineage (zu). His great great grandfather moved to Hangzhou, Qiantang xian. He and his elder brother, Tong [3736], established this family (jia) branch of the lineage by passing the jinshi exam. Kuo's [1450] and Pei's [1456] father, Fu's [7324] uncle, Gou's [1449] and Liao's [1453] granduncle, and Xu(4) Zhongrong's [7244] son-in-law. Zhejiang TZ, 123.20b; Wang Anshi, WJ, 98.1013; Zeng Gong, WJ, 45.6a-6b (wife, surname Xu(4), who died in 1068 at age 83). CBD, 1, 674.</note>
